\ncovering model may correspond to the two distinct regions of polarization\nobserved in the optical. Regardless of the physical model, spectral changes\nbetween epochs are driven by the absorption components and on short time scales\nby intrinsic AGN variability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Aug 2020 16:56:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-07"}
