edictions and exhibits\nimproved control performance, compared to a model that assumes homoscedastic\nuncertainty only, in the presence of varying degrees of input degradation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Aug 2020 21:04:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Jul 2022 04:45:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-12"}
