w Nicol (UoY), Gabriel Niculescu (JMU), Alexander Ostrovidov (FSU),\n  Zisis Papandreou (UR), KiJun Park (JLab), Eugene Pasyuk (JLab), Peter Pauli\n  (UoG), Lubomir Pentchev (JLab), William Phelps (CNU), John Price (CSU), Jorg\n  Reinhold (FIU), Dimitri Romanov (ITEP), Carlos Salgado (NSU), Todd Satogata\n  (Jlab), Susan Schadmand (Julich Center Hadron Phys.), Amy Schertz (W&M), Axel\n  Schmidt (GWU), Daniel Sober (CUA), Alexander Somov (JLab), Sergei Somov\n  (MEPhI), Victor Tarasov (ITEP), Simon Taylor (JLab), Annika Thiel (Bonn U.),\n  Guido Maria Urciuoli (I.N.F.N. Roma), Holly Szumila-Vance (GWU), Daniel Watts\n  (UoY), Lawrence Weinstein (ODU), Timothy Whitlatch (JLab), Nilanga\n  Wickramaarachchi (ODU), Bogdan Wojtsekhowski (JLab), Nicholas Zachariou\n  (UoY), Jonathan Zarling (UR), Jixie Zhang (UVa), Alexey Anisovich (Bonn U.),\n  Alexei Bazavov (MSU), Rene Bellwied (Houston U.), Veronique Bernard (U.\n  Paris-Sud), Gilberto Colangelo (Bern U.), Ales Cieply (Rez Nucl. Phys.\n  Inst.), Michael Doring (GWU), Ali Eskanderian (GWU), Jose Goity (Hampton U.),\n  Helmut Haberzettl (GWU), Mirza Hadzimehmedovic (Tuzla U.), Robert Jaffe\n  (MIT), Boris Kopeliovich (UTFSM), Heinrich Leutwyler (Bern U.), Maxim Mai\n  (GWU), Terry Mart (U. Indonesia), Maxim Matveev (PNPI), Ulf-G. Meissner (Bonn\n  U.), Colin Morningstar (CMU), Bachir Moussallam (U. Paris-Sud), Kanzo\n  Nakayama (UGA), Wolfgang Ochs (Max-Plank Inst.), Youngseok Oh (Kyungpook U.),\n  Rifat Omerovic (Tuzla U.), Hedim Osmanovic (Tuzla U.), Eulogio Oset (Valencia\n  U.), Antimo Palano (I.N.F.N Bari), Jose Pelaez (Madrid U.), Alessandro\n  Pilloni (ECT), Maxim Polyakov (Ruhr U.), David Richards (JLab), Arkaitz Rodas\n  (JLab), Dan-Olof Riska (Finnish Society Sci. and Lett.), Jacobo Ruiz de\n  Elvira (Bern U.), Hui-Young Ryu (Pusan U.), Elena Santopinto (I.N.F.N.\n  Genova), Andrey Sarantsev (Bonn U.), Jugoslav Stahov (Tuzla U.), Alfred Svarc\n  (Rudjer Boskovic Inst.), Adam Szczepaniak (IU), Ronald Workman (GW