ions and it is found that the peak levels of the\nspectral linewidth as a function of drive current agrees quantitatively with\ntypical levels found in experiments at room temperature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Aug 2020 10:05:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-30"}
