ined on reconstructed\nsurfaces in the nineties, and shed light on recent Kibble-Zurek experiments on\nthe period-3 phase of chains of Rydberg atoms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Aug 2020 12:55:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-20"}
