The results showcase that the\nproposed method achieves an increase in renewable self-consumption at building\nand community levels, as well as a reduction in electricity costs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Aug 2020 20:23:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2020 11:58:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-08"}
