 the ensemble classifier achieved the lowest precision, thus impairing\nits F1-measure (79.95% $\\pm$ 2.13), it was the most powerful classifier to\ndetect Aedes aegypti in our dataset.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Aug 2020 00:26:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-02"}
